WARNING! These lyrics are what fans remembered from the ArtRAVE: The ARTPOP Ball, and from the snippet. They are in no specific order
I don't remember much from last Sunday and I'm probably reaching"

"I'm not your Billie Jean"

"I could be your thriller

"You never know

The next Michael Jackson"

"So don't leave me yet."
